                     <interp inst="t18620818-831-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">of uttering. Recommended to mercy by the Jury.</hi>
                  </rs>
               </p>
